# Noetfield — ship bundle

**Conflict law:** [SKILL-007](../skills/SKILL-007-auto-conflict-resolution.md) · R-007/R-008/R-011 win over ship workflow.

## Triggers

- **`PLAN WITH NO ASF`** — pick via `make pick-wise` or `make pick-no-asf-plan`; read GTM_NEXT / SHIP_NOW
- **`implement`** — required before disk edits (founder order)

## Flow

0. SKILL-007 — without `implement`, stop after propose and **ASK**
1. Present ≤3 tasks from live queue ([LIVE-STATUS.md](../../reports/agent-auto/LIVE-STATUS.md))
2. After `implement`: one prompt or ≤3 Tier-A GTM tasks · branch `cursor/<slug>-37f0`
3. Verify: `make plan-with-no-asf-verify` · `make verify-gtm` · `make verify-agent-scope`
4. Sync status · [ingest YAML](noetfield-ingest-yaml.mdc) · **ASK** next move

## Ingest vs idle

| Ingest after ship | Required — does not block |
| Wait for next Prompt OS order mid-bundle | Forbidden |

Never self-start from `plan.json` alone. Never edit SourceA or SinaPromptOS.
